Example usages:

ttt 'Hello world!' > helloworld.ngc
ttt_dxf 'Hello world!' > helloworld.dxf
ttt -f /usr/share/fonts/truetype/ttf-bitstream-vera/VeraIt.ttf 'Hello!' > h.ngc

Notes:

linescale (-l) causes outlines to be filled with linear hatching.  24
is the minimum value == maximum spacing, renders with space between
lines for fine dry erase, 64 is nearly solid fill with fine dry erase.